              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\n\nAnd it says:\n\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_quote",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Solo independent researchers we know often discuss the challenge of working alone. Being part of a research group can create community, social accountability, provide feedback, and just give you someone to talk to when you’re feeling stuck or bored. This is why we started our Researchers-in-Residence program."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "\nWhich made me think \"this could be something we set up in FoC!\"\n\nAnd then I came right here to say that, without thinking it through any further..."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
